values:
I'm afraid so much is happening at once.&nbsp; I may be scarce for a while.&nbsp; Finals are comming up in school.&nbsp; This will include a guitar solo I must perform infront of an audiance (nervousness is setting in).&nbsp; I ofcourse over did it and choose a piece that I'm singing with.&nbsp; Also, I'm getting ready for transfer to another college.&nbsp; The only problem is I don't know when I'm leaving yet.&nbsp; The advisor keeps trying to get me to leave in January.&nbsp; I still have friends here.&nbsp; I have a life here that I will miss very much.&nbsp; I hurt, I don't know what to do.&nbsp; Of course then I suppose it will all be fine.&nbsp; Things will work out, no things definately will because I will see to it that they will.&nbsp; Times like this make me want a hot tea, a fire place, and still I would probably be soaking wet with tears.&nbsp; Tears are good right?&nbsp; They release the soul from pain?&nbsp; 

It snowed yesterday.&nbsp; I love the snow.&nbsp; Its so pretty.&nbsp; I want summer back, my heart yearns for it.&nbsp; The cold makes me feel so alone and blue.&nbsp; The heat still doesn't work well in my apartment.

~sighs~&nbsp; alas, back to playing my guitar.
